(3892, 1, '2015-12-08 01:52:13', '2015-12-08 01:52:13', '', 'R/C LINEAR 2SLOT DIFFUSER', '<span style="color: #428bca;font-size=11"><strong>Features</strong></span>\n<ul>\n	<li>This linear slot diffuser is an elongated outlet consisiting of a single or multiplenumber of slots to provide supply or return air in heating or cooling.</li>\n	<li>This linear slot diffuser is constructed from extruded aluminium section.</li>\n	<li>Maxinum 3000mm length in one modular section.</li>\n	<li>This linear slot is available with one to eight slots construction, standard slot widthis 20mm.</li>\n	<li>Finished with powder-coated white or natural anodized as the standard colors.</li>\n</ul>\n<strong><span style="color: #428bca;">Application</span></strong>\n<ul>\n	<li>This diffuser is suitable to be installed at ceiling, wall, sill and floor.</li>\n	<li>This diffuser is also for continuous "wall to wall" installations.</li>\n</ul>\n&nbsp;', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '3887-autosave-v1', '', '', '2015-12-08 01:52:13', '2015-12-08 01:52:13', '', 3887, 'http://www.qualitair.com.au/2015/12/08/3887-autosave-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
